Package: RiboseQC
Title: Ribo-seQC, a comprehensive Ribo-seq analysis tool
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(person("Lorenzo", "Calviello", email = "calviello.l.bio@gmail.com", role = c("aut")),
